headline: State of New Jersey Streamlines Property Tax Relief Program for Residents with New Solution from Tyler Technologies
summary: PLANO, Texas, March 11, 2025--Tyler Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: TYL) announced today it has launched a new property tax solution with the New Jersey Division of Taxation, allowing New Jersey residents to apply for three major property tax relief programs through a single streamlined application.
